reviewText: I sued to see him on TV on a comedy show. I've been trying to get his CD's for a couple of years. I am glad that I could find them. It is a joy to see him again and laugh out loud at his wild stories. He is a character like no other.

reviewText: Bruce Bruce warns you from the jump that he has no sense and is "stupid for real".  This comedy show is hilarious from beginning to end and is something that I have found never gets old.  He is one of the most under-rated comics in the game right now .... despite that I hope that he keeps it up because he brings laughter to an entirely different level whenever I watch him perform.
